metadata.title: Slope 1:250,000 - Southcentral
metadata.description: Data Type: Elevation;  This layer includes slope data covering South Central Alaska organized by 1:250,000 scale USGS quadrangles based on elevation data derived from digital elevation models (DEM) at 1:250,000 scale. The data is divided according to 250,000 scale quad boundaries Related data sets include: slope derived from 1:63,360 scale DEM's and elevation files.
